## Remarks  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/includes/deprecatedcontent-md.md)]  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="94af2-103">この属性は依存関係プロパティ オプションとしてのみ使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94af2-103">This attribute should only be used as dependency property option.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94af2-104">.NET プロパティで宣言しても無視されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94af2-104">Attributes are ignored if declared on a .NET property.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="94af2-105"><xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ValidationOptionAttribute> メタプロパティで使うことのみを意図したものです。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94af2-105">The <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ValidationOptionAttribute> is intended to be used on Meta-properties only.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94af2-106">インスタンス プロパティで使おうとしても無視されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94af2-106">It will be ignored for instance properties.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="94af2-107">詳細については、「[アクティビティプロパティの使用](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/974353d4-28f9-4202-890d-b36981876148)」を参照してください。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94af2-107">For more information, see [Using Activity Properties](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/974353d4-28f9-4202-890d-b36981876148) for more details.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="94af2-108"><xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ValidationOptionAttribute> を指定しない場合の既定の動作は <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ValidationOption.Optional?displayProperty=nameWithType> となります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="94af2-108">If the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ValidationOptionAttribute> is not specified, the behavior defaults to <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ValidationOption.Optional?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
public sealed partial class Activity1: Activity  
{  
    public Activity1()  
    {  
    }  
  
    public static DependencyProperty MyPropertyProperty =   
        DependencyProperty.Register(  
            "MyProperty",   
            typeof(string),   
            typeof(Activity1),  
            new PropertyMetadata(  
                DependencyPropertyOptions.Metadata,  
                new ValidationOptionAttribute(ValidationOption.Required)));  
  
    [Browsable(true)]  
    [DesignerSerializationVisibility(DesignerSerializationVisibility.Visible)]  
    public string MyProperty  
    {  
        get  
        {  
            return ((string)(base.GetValue(Activity1.MyPropertyProperty)));  
        }  
        set  
        {  
            base.SetValue(Activity1.MyPropertyProperty, value);  
        }  
    }  
}  
```
